-- Exxaro Resources Says Most Funding for Grootegeluk Mine Expansion Secured
-- Carli Lourens
-- 2010-06-18T06:59:49Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-18/exxaro-resources-says-most-funding-for-grootegeluk-mine-expansion-secured.html

          
          
             Exxaro Resources Ltd. has secured
most of the funding required for the expansion of its Grootgeluk
coal mine, the company said in a statement handed to reporters
today in Lephalale, northern South Africa.  
 The company plans to spend 4.5 billion rand ($596.5
million) on the project by May 2012, while the total cost of the
project is 9.5 billion rand, it said.  
 To contact the reporter on this story:
Carli Lourens in Lephalale at 
 clourens@bloomberg.net   
          
          


  


        